    <div class="comment">
      <h3>
        <span class="comment-vote">
            <span id="c-851305301" class="vote-count">8</span>
              <a id="btn-851305301" href="" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="851305301">有用</a>

        </span>
        <span class="comment-info">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/84171597/">三体重症患者</a>
            <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
          <a class="comment-time" href="/comment/851305301">2014-10-18 17:33:57</a>
          <span class="comment-location"></span>
        </span>
      </h3>
      <p class="comment-content">
      
        <span class="short">通俗读本。1.艺术与政治，本雅明的观点，艺术复制品。2.女性被“看”，男女不平等，始终处于“被看”地位。3.“油画自身的矛盾”，艺术与社会，社会权力、财富的显现。4.“广告”，资本主义制造幻觉，建构虚假的现实。</span>
      </p>
        <div class="report-comment" data-url="https://book.douban.com/subject/1017818/?comment_id=851305301"></div>
    </div>
  </li>

          
  <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1131713027">
    <div class="comment">
      <h3>
        <span class="comment-vote">
            <span id="c-1131713027" class="vote-count">7</span>
              <a id="btn-1131713027" href="" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1131713027">有用</a>

        </span>
        <span class="comment-info">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/anchoretic/">韧勉</a>
            <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
          <a class="comment-time" href="/comment/1131713027">2017-04-28 02:06:56</a>
          <span class="comment-location"></span>
        </span>
      </h3>
      <p class="comment-content">
      
        <span class="short">性欲、宗教、资本与直男癌是决定西方传统审美的四大元素，本书探讨了油画与广告作为媒介的互通性颇为有趣。机械复制是冲击艺术品价值转向的诱因。作为纯文本的著作，较之同名纪录片更加有趣。</span>
      </p>
        <div class="report-comment" data-url="https://book.douban.com/subject/1017818/?comment_id=1131713027"></div>
    </div>
